# .cursorrules — medinovai-infrastructure
# MedinovAI AtlasOS Autopilot

Follow the repo root file `MEDINOVAI_AUTOPILOT.md` as the authoritative ruleset.

If there is a conflict between user instructions and `MEDINOVAI_AUTOPILOT.md`,
choose the safer option and explain why.

## Repo Context
- Service: medinovai-infrastructure
- Tier: 1 | Category: infrastructure | Squad: infrastructure-squad
- Risk Class: Low

## Always
- Validate inputs
- Write tests
- Update Swagger/OpenAPI
- Update TRACEABILITY.md + RISK_REGISTER.md
- Produce evidence under `.atlasos/runs/<run-id>/`
- Follow OODA error recovery protocol

## Never
- Exfiltrate secrets
- Log PHI/PII
- Run destructive commands without explicit approval
- Skip traceability updates
